springMVC-请求

#### 1.请求参数的获取

##### 参数的类型

###### ①普通类型

访问的url地址： 

http://localhost/requestParam1?name=wyg&age=23



```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam1")
public String requestParam1(String name ,String age){
    System.out.println("name="+name+",age="+age);
    return "page.jsp";
}
```



**@RequestParam**

形参注解
**请求参数**与**形参**间的关系  

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam2")
public String requestParam2(
    @RequestParam(
		name = "userName",
		required = true,//是否强制赋值
		defaultValue = "itheima")//默认名字

 		String name
 		)
{
    	System.out.println("name="+name);
    	return "page.jsp";
}
```

###### ②POJO类型

实体类 

访问URL： http://localhost/requestParam3?name=wyg&age=14 

参数名称与POJO类属性名一致

```java
public class User {
	private String name;
    private Integer age;
}
```

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam3")
public String requestParam3(User user){
    System.out.println("name="+user.getName());
    return "page.jsp";
}
```



**参数冲突**

将被同时赋值

访问URL： http://localhost/requestParam4?name=itheima&**age**=14  

```java
public class User {
	private String name;
    private Integer age;
}
```



```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam4")
public String requestParam4(User user,String age){
    System.out.println("user.age="+user.getAge()+",age="+age); //aged都会进行传参
    return "page.jsp";
}
```

**复杂POJO类型参数**

参数名称与对象层次结构名称保持一致

  访问URL： http://localhost/requestParam5?address.pro=beijing  

```java
public class User {
	private String name;
    private Integer age;
    private Address address;
}
```

```java
public class Address {
	private String pro;
    private Integer city;
    private String address;
}
```

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam5")
public String requestParam5(User user){
    System.out.println("user.address="+user.getAddress().getProvince());
    return "page.jsp";
}
```



**对象的属性出现集合的时候**

访问URL： [http://localhost/requestParam7?addresses[0].province=bj&addresses[1].province=tj](http://localhost/requestParam7?addresses[0].province=bj&addresses[1].province=tj)

```java
public class User {
    private String name;
    private Integer age;
    private List<Address> addresses;
}

public class Address {
    private String province;
    private String city;
    private String address;
}
```

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam7")
public String requestParam7(User user){
    System.out.println("user.addresses="+user.getAddress());
    return "page.jsp";
}
```

对象的属性出现Map集合的时候**Map**

访问URL： [http://localhost/requestParam8?addressMap[’home’].province=bj&addressMap[’job’].province=tj](http://localhost/requestParam8?addressMap[’home’].province=bj&addressMap[’job’].province=tj  )  

```java
public class User {
    private String name;
    private Integer age;
    private Map<String,Address> addressMap;
}
public class Address {
    private String province;
    private String city;
    private String address;
}
```

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam8")
public String requestParam8(User user){
    System.out.println("user.addressMap="+user.getAddressMap());
    return "page.jsp";
}
```



###### ③数组类型参数

参数名>>>处理器方法形参名 保持一致

<u>http://localhost/requestParam9?nick=Jockme&nick=zahc</u>  

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam9")
public String requestParam9(String[] nick){
    System.out.println(nick[0]+","+nick[1]);
    return "page.jsp";
}
```

###### ④集合的类型参数

请求参数名>>>处理器方法形参名保持一致

请求参数数量＞ 大于1个

http://localhost/requestParam10?nick=Jockme&nick=zahc

```java
@RequestMapping("/requestParam10")
public String requestParam10(@RequestParam("nick") List<String> nick){
    System.out.println(nick);
    return "page.jsp";
}
```















